docs.snippet: Further softening of the Canadian dollar represented the only significant variation in foreign currency values last week. On Friday remittance on the Dominion fell to 85.68 cents, lowest since April 1, with the close on Saturday at 86 cents, a loss...
docs.lead_paragraph: Further softening of the Canadian dollar represented the only significant variation in foreign currency values last week. On Friday remittance on the Dominion fell to 85.68 cents, lowest since April 1, with the close on Saturday at 86 cents, a loss of 5/8 cent from the preceding week, and 2 1/2 cents since the beginning of December.

docs.snippet: RIO DE JANEIRO, Brazil, Dec. 30 (AP) -- Brazilian State police and organized Nazis have clashed "with some dead" in the State of Rio Grande do Sul, where more than half a million Germans live, and many fifth columnists have been arrested, said...
docs.lead_paragraph: RIO DE JANEIRO, Brazil, Dec. 30 (AP) -- Brazilian State police and organized Nazis have clashed "with some dead" in the State of Rio Grande do Sul, where more than half a million Germans live, and many fifth columnists have been arrested, said dispatches from Porto Alegre today.

headline.main: NAZIS FIGHT POLICE IN SOUTH OF BRAZIL; ' Some Dead' in Round-Up of Uniformed Germans in Rio Grande do Sul URUGUAY BARES A THREAT ' Alpine Regiment' Said to Get Orders From Rome -- Von Thermann Recall Is Denied
